- 方法二：设置ssl session缓存

配置实例:

```nginx
server { 
	listen 443; 
	server_name ....; 

	keepalive_time 100; // 设置超时时间 

	ssl on; 
	ssl_session_cache shared:SSL:10m; 
	ssl_session_timeout 10m; 

	ssl_certificate ....; 
	ssl certificate_key ....; 
	.... 
}
```

